44:54.616 --> 44:57.310
No, honey, not me.

44:57.410 --> 44:59.396
I was married.

44:59.496 --> 45:04.234
Back then you... you didn't do it
with someone else if you were married.

45:04.334 --> 45:07.423
Yeah, I think I read
something about that.

45:12.217 --> 45:15.258
Who was he? Your husband.

45:21.434 --> 45:22.898
Michael.

45:29.025 --> 45:32.325
Five, six, seven, eight...

45:34.781 --> 45:36.862
