59:01.921 --> 59:04.532
- Merrill, who am I supposed to be?
- Scheherazade.

59:04.632 --> 59:07.683
I look like Sabu on a bad night.

59:09.095 --> 59:12.999
- Hey, Ma. Neat costume.
- Merrill, do something with this.

59:13.099 --> 59:15.180
I wanna talk to you.

59:20.732 --> 59:22.813
Come here.

59:23.568 --> 59:26.278
I'd like you to read something.

59:29.657 --> 59:31.739
Go ahead. Read it.

59:34.412 --> 59:37.732
