01:02:02.268 --> 01:02:04.349
Go, four.

01:02:13.780 --> 01:02:16.454
Dolly around, three. Right... take four.

01:02:25.792 --> 01:02:28.904
Listen, I really want you
to lay off Danny. I'm serious.

01:02:29.004 --> 01:02:32.532
- What do you mean?
- All this fake man-to-man bullshit.

01:02:32.632 --> 01:02:34.951
- It's not bullshit.
- Yes, it is.

01:02:35.051 --> 01:02:37.621
He's 13 years old,
not one of your poker buddies.

01:02:37.721 --> 01:02:40.749
- You're smothering him.
- You fill his head full of crap.

01:02:40.849 --> 01:02:44.127
- Such as what?
- Don't study, life's a big party...

01:02:44.227 --> 01:02:46.805
- Sounds good to me.
- Oh, yeah?

01:02:47.814 --> 01:02:50.842
You got three daughters.
Give them your wisdom.

01:02:50.942 --> 01:02:55.138
- My wisdom is for a son.
- Don't break my heart.

01:02:55.238 --> 01:02:57.766
How long's it been?
Eight years Michael's dead?

01:02:57.866 --> 01:03:02.331
- You shut up.
- No. You let me talk. Enough is enough.

01:03:03.538 --> 01:03:06.983
The boy needs a father, a man in his life,
someone he can talk to.

01:03:07.083 --> 01:03:10.320
- Somebody who can teach him.
- How to screw the chorus girls?

01:03:10.420 --> 01:03:13.198
Why not, if he wants to? Get off me!

01:03:13.298 --> 01:03:18.119
