- It's OK, son.

01:30:25.491 --> 01:30:27.572
Come on.

01:30:29.621 --> 01:30:34.169
He's a monster! Come to me! Come to Mom.

01:30:34.834 --> 01:30:36.319
Mom...

01:30:36.419 --> 01:30:40.671
You can't have him!
You keep your hands off my son!

01:30:52.852 --> 01:30:54.933
It's OK, son. It's OK.

01:31:02.195 --> 01:31:06.266
I believe that our generation
will change the world.

01:31:06.366 --> 01:31:09.490
I believe in freedom and honour,

01:31:10.995 --> 01:31:15.247
hard work and the genius
of the American system.

01:31:17.001 --> 01:31:23.825
I believe in the need to protect that system
with strength and justice and compassion

01:31:23.925 --> 01:31:26.619
wherever it is threatened.

01:31:26.719 --> 01:31:32.644
I believe in respect for rank
and the wisdom of our founding fathers.

01:31:34.352 --> 01:31:36.433
I believe in America.

01:31:38.189 --> 01:31:44.315
To love it and defend it as my father did
with the ultimate sacrifice.

01:31:47.365 --> 01:31:50.977
I believe in the importance of family,

01:31:51.077 --> 01:31:54.914
in my mother and her spirit.

01:32:02.672 --> 01:32:07.422
What the hell could I do?
There was Eddie every time I turned around.

01:32:09.762 --> 01:32:14.061
And you know what? Danny loved him.

01:32:15.977 --> 01:32:19.005
I never had a chance.

01:32:19.105 --> 01:32:22.444
- And you and Eddie?
- We hardly spoke.

01:32:24.986 --> 01:32:29.599
Network dropped me like a hot potato.
They said I was...

01:32:29.699 --> 01:32:32.644
- Controversial?
- Bingo.

01:32:32.744 --> 01:32:35.688
That was me. Isn't that a hoot?

01:32:35.788 --> 01:32:42.792
Me, who always thought Karl Marx
was the sixth Marx brother after Zeppo.

01:32:44.130 --> 01:32:48.201
Eddie stayed with the show but...
it never really worked.

01:32:48.301 --> 01:32:50.411
Cancelled him after a season.

01:32:50.511 --> 01:32:54.514
- So what did you do?
- What did I do? What didn't I do?

01:32:55.892 --> 01:33:01.256
Dinner theatre, stock, club dates.

01:33:01.356 --> 01:33:06.678
Saved up a little money, bought myself
a little bistro in Hollywood.

01:33:06.778 --> 01:33:09.472
A jazz club.

01:33:09.572 --> 01:33:12.475
I liked it. Friends would come by.

01:33:12.575 --> 01:33:14.656
And Danny?

01:33:19.916 --> 01:33:21.568
Danny.

01:33:24.254 --> 01:33:28.636
- Bring him back here,
- Remember to stop the bleeding!

01:33:31.553 --> 01:33:37.181
